BLAH
end note
}

a1s1 --> a1s2a
a1s2a --> a1s2b
a1s2b --> a1s3




rectangle Act2 as "Act 2: Cairo" {
usecase "Dept of Antiquities" as a2s1
note left
BLAH
end note
