note left
BLAH
end note
usecase "Desert chase" as a3s3
note left
BLAH
end note
usecase "Train" as a3s4
note left
BLAH
end note
}

a3s1 --> a3s2
a3s2 --> a3s3
a3s3 --> a3s4

